snippet.textDisplay: 7 months ago was the last time Claire made a normal episode of her just cooking a nice recipe, no challenge or fuss added. It was Claire Makes Angel Food Cake. I know her 'Make Gourmet' videos really bring in the views but she knows so much about cooking. When she tells a recipe she breaks it down like no one else can and that really helped me not only learning why but how a lot of things in cooking happen. Wish my favorite chef wasn't only doing one show and had breaks at least.
